snippet.title: Mind Power Audio
snippet.description:
Channel about Self help/self development,self hypnosis and New self improvement techniques, NLP, Law of Attraction, Manifestation,

Manifestation is based on The Law of Attraction, which, in simple terms, is the ability to bring things into our realities through energetic attraction. Essentially, like attracts like, what you are putting out into the world is what you will receive back from it.
